# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# SelfDiary — Git Line Ending Normalization
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ensure consistent LF line endings in the repository,
# regardless of OS. Git will convert CRLF to LF on commit.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly mark binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
